short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add a simple timer to your Google Meet sessions.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension shows a timer during meetings. It keeps time even if the meeting was restarted or inactive for up to 5 minutes. 

This extension does not track any user data so no privacy policy is provided.
